In the Matter of The Application of Gussie Goldman Woods for a Writ of Habeas Corpus
To the Clerk of the above Entitled Court:

You will please enter an apperance as attorneys for petitioner in the above entitled cause, and service of all subsequent papers, except writs and process, may be made upon said petitioner, by leaving the same with
Vanderveer & Cummings Office Address 813-815 Hogs Bdlg. Seattle, Wash
